law.history: Repealed 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 77, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 552, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 318, sec. 261, effective July 15, 1996. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2636-6b.
